overview:
Badawneh Medical Services has been established in 1990, 70 km north of Amman-Jordan. Badawneh Medical Services consists of high-qualified staff, which make it capable of managing, dealing and handling services in middle east and nabouring countries.

Badawneh Medical Services imports and distributes the following products: .Medical supplies and equipment’s. .Dental supplies and equipment’s. Badawneh Medical Services has 19 years experience of importing products from European countries, China, Taiwan, Korea, Pakistan and USA.

Every products undergoes inspection in order to satisfy the requirement of our customers and hence giving the class one services and maintaining the standard quality by providing the New Technology which helps in giving the result accurately

We are specialist in supplying products to the hospitals (public/private) and all clinics. If you are looking for high-quality products, efficient deals and accuracy, please don’t hesitate to contact us for any further information
